msgstr "Ashley Boyd<br/><i>Vice President, Advocacy and Engagement<br/>Mozilla Foundation<br/><br/></i>Gennie Gebhart<br/><i>Associate Director of Research<br/>Electronic Frontier Foundation</i>"
